	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Can you make your scanline emulator emulate part-of-a-scanline? If so, it'd be easy to bring it up to pixel accuracy. Start by simply running the CPU ahead of the PPU and then having the PPU catch up to the CPU on every CPU$2xxx write. See which games screw up under that.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


